@BookFastApiHost = http://localhost:5096
@SeedRoomId = 8C2D3CFD-2F3A-4C72-9F5B-7397C1D4B901

### Health
GET {{BookFastApiHost}}/health
Accept: application/json

### List rooms
GET {{BookFastApiHost}}/api/v1/rooms
Accept: application/json

### Check room availability
GET {{BookFastApiHost}}/api/v1/rooms/{{SeedRoomId}}/availability?fromUtc=2026-05-01T09:00:00Z&toUtc=2026-05-01T10:00:00Z
Accept: application/json

### Create reservation
POST {{BookFastApiHost}}/api/v1/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "{{SeedRoomId}}",
  "reservedBy": "integration-demo@bookfast.local",
  "purpose": "Portfolio walkthrough",
  "startUtc": "2026-05-01T09:00:00Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-05-01T10:00:00Z"
}

### GraphQL rooms query
POST {{BookFastApiHost}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query Rooms($first: Int!) { rooms(first: $first) { id code name location capacity amenities } }",
  "variables": {
    "first": 5
  }
}
